296,622441|title=The Winners From The ESPY Awards|page=2C|newspaper=[[St. Petersburg Times]]|date=July 17, 2007|accessdate=November 23, 2011}}</ref>\n|1\n|2007\n|-\n|Inductee in Kalamazoo Central High School Athletic Hall of Fame<ref name=\"Mack\"/>\n|1\n|2007\n|-\n|[[Baseball Digest]] Player of the Year<ref name=jeterbio/>\n|1\n|2006\n|-\n|[[GIBBY Awards]] Hitter of the Year Award<ref name=jeterbio/>\n|1\n|2006\n|-\n|Baseball America 1st-Team Major League All-Star (SS)<ref name=jeterbio/>\n|1\n|2006\n|-\n|[[GIBBY Awards]] Play of the Year<ref name=mlbbio/>\n|1\n|2004\n|-\n|[[Players Choice Award]] Rookie of the Year<ref name=mlbbio/>\n|1\n|2004\n|-\n|''[[The Sporting News]]'' \"Good Guy in Sports\" Award<ref name=\"mlbbio\">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player_career.jsp?player_id=116539|title=Derek Jeter: Biography and Career Highlights|publisher=MLB.com|accessdate=August 9, 2009}}</ref>\n|1\n|2002\n|-\n||[[ESPY Awards]] [[Best Play ESPY Award]]<ref name=mlbbio/>\n|1\n|2002\n|-\n|[[Babe Ruth Award]]<ref name=mlbbio/>\n|1\n|2000\n|-\n|[[Major League Baseball All-Star Game Most Valuable Player Award|All-Star Game Most Valuable Player Award]]<ref name=jeterbio/>\n|1\n|2000\n|-\n|[[World Series Most Valuable Player Award]]<ref name=jeterbio/>\n|1\n|2000\n|-\n|[[Joan Payson]] Award for Community Service<ref>{{cite news|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courant/access/28247193.html?dids=28247193:28247193&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Mar+29%2C+1998&author=JACK+O'CONNELL%3B+Courant+Staff+Writer&pub=Hartford+Courant&desc=JETER+KNOWS+KEY+TO+THE+CITY+YANKEES+SHORTSTOP+IS+CAREFUL+NOT+TO+GET+CAUGHT+UP+IN+IT&pqatl=google|title=Jeter Knows Key to the City: Yankees Shortstop Is Careful Not To Get Caught Up In It|newspaper=[[Hartford Courant]]|first=Jack|last=O'Connell|page=E.1|date=March 29, 1998|accessdate=November 19, 2011}} {{Subscription required|date=November 2011}}</ref>\n|1\n|1997\n|-\n|AL [[Major League Baseball Rookie of the Year Award|Rookie of the Year